info.title: PSGC API
info.description:
Current data is as of June 30, 2022. Data is based from https://psa.gov.ph/classification/psgc/ (Publication file).

Limitation: The content-type header of the API is text/html instead of application/json. Use API JSON call if content-type header application/json is needed

Issues/request/suggestions: Kindly file your concern here https://gitlab.com/psgc/api/issues
